\"from\": 5555, \"to\": 5718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5632, \"end\": 5641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jake Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's won Wimbledon seven times, not saying the Wimbledon final is not the pinnacle of our sport.\", \"from\": 5720, \"to\": 5817, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I felt like this meant more, just based on feelings.\", \"from\": 5818, \"to\": 5874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think Wimbledon helped, and I think he was healthy going in, and he was pretty honest about it.\", \"from\": 5876, \"to\": 5974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5885, \"end\": 5894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"score\": 0.6230557776772512, \"rank\": 0.3968162261393032, \"text\": \"Wimbledon\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Wimbledon_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He said like, 'I feel better here than I did at Wimbledon by far.'\", \"from\": 5976, \"to\": 6043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LATEST SPORTS NEWS:  Novak Djokovic beat Carlos Alcaraz in straight sets to win his first gold medal at the Olympics  REUTERS  \\\"He knew that his best chance at a medal, and we said this in the weird quasi-Olympic show from last week, he did not mess around with doubles, he did not stay in the village.\", \"from\": 6045, \"to\": 6347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6066, \"end\": 6080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_